| Term / Acronym      | Description                                                |
| ------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- |
| **BBMS**            | Blood Bank Management System                               |
| **Donor**           | A registered individual who donates blood                  |
| **Blood Inventory** | Record of available blood units by group and quantity      |
| **Administrator**   | Authorized user responsible for managing system operations |
| **QA**              | Quality Assurance                                          |
| **SRS**             | Software Requirements Specification                        |
| **UI**              | User Interface                                             |
| **DBMS**            | Database Management System                                 |
